('98334','33931','5','Land with project for a modern sea view villa in Sol de Mallorca'),
('98335','33932','5','Sol de Mallorca is located in the southwest of Mallorca in the municipality of Calvia. International schools, golf courses, marinas, restaurants and Palma de Mallorca are only a few minutes by car away. On a 1.500m² flat seaview plot, a modern villa was planned. Star of construction will be spring 2016 and mid-2017, the Villa sould be ready to move in. The approx 320m² constructed area is distributed over 2 residential floors. In the living area you enter the villa over an entrance hall, followed by living-dining room, modern fitted kitchen, utility room, guest toilet, guest bedroom with bathroom en suite. On the 1st floor there are 2 bedrooms with a bathroom en suite and a terrace with an outdoor staircase leading to the pool and the garden. In addition, the villa offers more 120m² basement, including 2 underground parking spaces, engine room and store room. At this stage, the buyer can still have an influence on the selection of materials'),
